        "description": {
          "chat": "",
          "unidentified": "",
          "value": "<p>The very act of observing the Seen changes the creature on a molecular level. Whether a creature (or magic or technological sensor) is observing the Seen changes its abilities and statistics as follows.</p>\n<p><em>Observed</em>: While the Seen is observed by any non-Seen creature, magic, or technological sensor, its speed is 30 feet and it is corporeal. It can also attempt Stealth checks to hide in plain sight.</p>\n<p><em>Unobserved</em>: While nothing is directly observing the Seen, its speed is 60 feet and it is incorporeal.</p>"
